    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive masterpiece in truly pristine condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, maintained to a showroom standard that defies its age. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a history of uncompromising care. Mechanically synchronized to perfection and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning driver who refuses to settle for anything less than the absolute best. Experience the confidence of owning a vehicle that looks, feels, and performs exactly as the manufacturer intended.",
      "price": 48500.0,
