    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Slide into the driver's seat and let the scent of aged mahogany and hand-stitched leather transport you to a simpler era of elegance. This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule of European craftsmanship, humming with a rhythmic heart that yearns for the open road. Every curve of its silhouette catches the light like a sculpted masterpiece, promising a journey where the destination matters far less than the soul-stirring symphony of the drive itself. A true connoisseur\u2019s dream, preserved in a state of grace, waiting for its next great chapter.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom-fresh condition. This specimen has been curated with obsessive attention to detail, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Mechanically impeccable and documented with a comprehensive service history, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice. Experience the peace of mind that comes with a vehicle maintained to the highest possible standards.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
