    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, always keeping her tucked away in the garage and hand-washed every weekend. She\u2019s in truly stunning shape\u2014honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish on her. It drives like a dream and still has that 'new car' feel that gets your heart racing. I\u2019m only letting her go to a good home where she'll be just as appreciated. Come by for a coffee and a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
