    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a turn-key specimen of peak mechanical synergy. This chassis has been curated with an uncompromising focus on drivetrain harmonics and structural rigidity. The naturally aspirated power unit exhibits perfect stoichiometric balance, benefiting from a comprehensive top-end overhaul including precision-shimmied valves and a high-flow cooling system to mitigate heat soak during spirited operation. We\u2019ve optimized the unsprung mass with lightweight forged alloys, while the subframe has been reinforced to eliminate common torsional stress fatigue. The limited-slip differential provides instantaneous torque vectoring, and the gearbox offers tactile, short-throw engagement with zero synchro drag. This is a zero-compromise, 'collector-grade' asset for the enthusiast who understands the value of meticulous service intervals and optimized power-to-weight ratios.",
